                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6972" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1085</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8088 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">面对贝壳，浑水是否“大失水准”？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">In the face of BEKE, has the Muddy Waters Research lost its standard?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">董秀良，鞠艳彬，宋玥琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贝壳找房（北京）科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中概股；做空危机；贝壳找房；浑水机构</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">China Concept Stock，Short selling，BEKE，Muddy Waters Research</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，赴美上市中概股屡遭重创，以浑水公司为首的专业做空机构对之虎视眈眈，这一次，浑水的“枪口”瞄向了贝壳找房。2021年12月16日，浑水调研机构发布了一份针对贝壳找房的77页做空报告，指控其存在虚增交易额与佣金收入、夸大门店数和经纪人数以及虚假收购等行为，一时引发贝壳投资者信任危机。贝壳找房24小时内连发两则声明就浑水相关质疑一一回应，贝壳股价基本恢复至做空前水平。本案例梳理了由链家转型而来的贝壳找房上市后进入行业冷淡期，随后遭浑水调研机构做空及贝壳反击的来龙去脉，并对做空危机过后的贝壳市场表现以及持续调查自证清白的过程进行描写，以此说明做空的过程及影响，旨在引导学生深入思考做空过程及反做空的相关理论与知识点，并对中国上市企业预防和应对做空危机有所启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, Chinese concept stocks listed in the United States have been hit hard, and professional short-selling institutions headed by Muddy Waters have been eyeing them. On December 16, 2021, Muddy Waters Research Institute released a 77-page short-selling report on BEKE, accusing it of inflating transaction volume and commission income, exaggerating the number of stores and brokers, and false acquisitions, which causing a crisis of trust among investors. BEKE issued two statements within 24 hours in response to Muddy Waters&#39; questions one by one, and the share price of BEKE has basically recovered to previous level. This case describes how BEKE, which was transformed from Lianjia, entered a lull in the industry after its IPO, and then was shorted by Muddy Waters Research Institute and BEKE fought back,and describes BEKE&#39;s market performance after the short-selling crisis and the investigation to clear its name, in order to explain the process and impact of short-selling, aiming to guide students deeply think about the relevant theories and knowledge points of the short-selling process and anti-shorting, and have enlightening significance for Chinese listed companies to prevent and respond to short-selling crises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《投资银行学》、《证券投资学》、《危机管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">做空的含义；做空机构做空的动机和着手点；做空机构盈利模式；做空产业链；中概股的含义及中概股公司被做空的原因；反做空的对策与步骤；企业遭受做空后常见的应对措施；信息不对称理论；信号传递理论；危机管理理论；企业危机管理机制与其他应急机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
